column5: Moose showed up while two Thunder Bay fisherman were trying there luck. Video and story below. https://www.tbnewswatch.com/local-ne...hermen-3603699https://youtu.be/JuUSVGMQf0k

Several years ago, while sitting in a cabin on O'Sullivan Lake, near Nakina, a female moose strolled into the camp and walked within 10 feet of our front door. Having enough of us- we were sitting at the table- it sauntered it's way all through the camp and then disappeared back into the woods. Closest I've ever been to a moose! Bill
